title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1982-05-23
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street-> Promised Land, They Love Each Other, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Loser-> Little Red Rooster, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums*-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> I Need A Miracle-> Casey Jones, E: Satisfaction, E: Brokedown Palace

*Miked a Harley Davidson Motorcycle during drums

reviews.review_text:
Grate Show and Great Matrix Really energetic show. I really enjoy this matrix because Bob’s guitar is really upfront in the mix. Jerry’s guitar is low in the mix in Shakedown and Promised Land but does even out for a really nice sounding recording. 
One of my favorites. Thanks, Hunter!
